function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.12') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.12!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != 'f55b9196e4c3aa2a48f93808fada0ba9ec053909') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'f55b9196e4c3aa2a48f93808fada0ba9ec053909') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '2bf4fb5f22528a1bc08023e52479074618850df5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== 'f55b9196e4c3aa2a48f93808fada0ba9ec053909') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') != '78ca1eb5e933327979c532e9c461df011f9f73f2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') !== '78ca1eb5e933327979c532e9c461df011f9f73f2') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') !== '182385da75856d8d32a605061a0b73bf1a73a332') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio') !== '78ca1eb5e933327979c532e9c461df011f9f73f2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.drawio');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') != '83faebdd2ee0a2120a96ea490e419d7901b671ae') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') !== '83faebdd2ee0a2120a96ea490e419d7901b671ae') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') !== '6e851b73053cf4965d28ddd7ee6f909700509a16') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png') !== '83faebdd2ee0a2120a96ea490e419d7901b671ae') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/database_connectivity_diagram.png');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') != '549778a0749084e6e6c3debaf31ca0fe04ffc4c9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');

		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '549778a0749084e6e6c3debaf31ca0fe04ffc4c9') {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '549778a0749084e6e6c3debaf31ca0fe04ffc4c9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_11();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != 'ddc9163dae7be9dc9a5fc975e9024663cb48f07d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'ddc9163dae7be9dc9a5fc975e9024663cb48f07d') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '44a8625bff6c56d010f54ad36c823771e35d8f66') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'ddc9163dae7be9dc9a5fc975e9024663cb48f07d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != '48a67bc9b63f78d2ef5f2e1af79a827f178f556b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '48a67bc9b63f78d2ef5f2e1af79a827f178f556b') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '781fafa0ff1b4e9cdb176ad66915d882ee45bea7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '48a67bc9b63f78d2ef5f2e1af79a827f178f556b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != 'fdf99db6a156e409c4f741ccd1f2be340a77837f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');

			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'fdf99db6a156e409c4f741ccd1f2be340a77837f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md') != 'de17439b721773e2cb5d0164847b50efe922127a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md') !== 'de17439b721773e2cb5d0164847b50efe922127a') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md') !== '55e17b3a7edf2b2e8e0dbba450c0c5e44fb5a297') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md') !== 'de17439b721773e2cb5d0164847b50efe922127a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/README.md');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php') != 'e8977924eceffa719f033f02964daf58011a2f80') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php') !== 'e8977924eceffa719f033f02964daf58011a2f80') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php') !== '130826ad81bc0a1687ba96cf135f2568eeba7f3a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/phpseclib/phpseclib/phpseclib/Crypt/Common/AsymmetricKey.php');

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
